
Roadmap:

 *** SimpleBusiness 1.x
     ==================

(1) data abstraction improvements
(2) setup page
(3) projection and selection support for IObjectSet
(4) export to PDF
(5) mailing facility -- when there is new issued invoice, send it to the customer's mailbox
(6) auto-invoice facility -- scheduled invoices -- for examle when you
provide a service and you want to get the same money each month...

 *** SimpleBusiness 2.x
     ==================

(1) Digital signature (!!!)
(2) Communication with bank to check if there's no unpaid invoice
(3) DEC/EDI (??)

